"{\"uid\": \"businessinsider.com-parents-teens-competing-science-fair-olympics-parenting-principles-advice-2024-6\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Teen geniuswas on full display at the Los Angeles Convention Center in mid-May.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 79, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Convention_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Convention Center\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Convention_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Convention_Center\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thousands of high-school students dressed in business wear showed off their robots, inventions, discoveries, andscientific experiments.\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They had all won regional, state, or national science fairs andfinally made it to theRegeneron International Science and Engineering Fair (ISEF) to compete for $9 million in prizes.\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers of the event call ISEF \\\"the Olympics of science fairs.\\\"\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just getting to ISEF is enough to make any parent proud.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not all theseexceptional Gen Zstudents have accomplished, though.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of them also play musical instruments, make art, or dance competitively.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Business Insider spoke with three ISEF parents about what they did to encourage their children's ambitions.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Business Insider\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had five key takeaways.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can take a lot of patience to keep responding when a kid peppers you with questions, but Smriti Motwani says she and her husband made that a priority with their son Divij.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smriti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Smriti\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smriti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smriti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My husband always treated him like an adult.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He would explain it to him like he's talking to an adult, and so I think that helped,\\\" Motwani, a cybersecurity executive, told BI.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3592646868491829e-11, \"text\": \"BI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His curiosity has taken him a long way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Divij, now 17, won first in ISEF's biomedical engineering category alongside his friend Ayush Garg for an AI dental exam the duo developed.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISEF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\"}, {\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.480913925749753e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maria Estrada also prioritized questions from her two kids, Pauline and John, who have both won awards at ISEF.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"score\": 0.9979062635693382, \"rank\": 0.0013107576918946681, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}, {\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"score\": 0.7953820283154115, \"rank\": 0.17127396054660346, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\"}, {\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Fowler\", \"score\": 0.9995689136930781, \"rank\": 0.0004311084785331499, \"text\": \"Pauline\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Fowler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Fowler\"}, {\"begin\": 1460, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISEF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Estrada did not know the answer, she would take the questioning kid to her husband.\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"score\": 0.7953820283154115, \"rank\": 0.17127396054660346, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he did not know either, the family would look it up together.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I taught them to look for it and research for it, not just rely on me,\\\" Estrada, who is a plant-science lecturer at Fresno State, told BI.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"score\": 0.7953820283154115, \"rank\": 0.17127396054660346, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\"}, {\"begin\": 1736, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fresno_State_Bulldogs_football\", \"score\": 0.9999721247046962, \"rank\": 2.7868072008821166e-05, \"text\": \"Fresno State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fresno_State_Bulldogs_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fresno_State_Bulldogs_football\"}, {\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3592646868491829e-11, \"text\": \"BI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All three parents who spoke with BI said they let their kids try different activities and follow what they enjoyed.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3592646868491829e-11, \"text\": \"BI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The students gained some independence and ended up busy with well-rounded extracurriculars that were fun for them.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Estrada's daughter, for example, balances her science hobbies with competitive ballet.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1993, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"score\": 0.7953820283154115, \"rank\": 0.17127396054660346, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Motwani's son edits a student magazine and sings in his high school choir when he's not tinkering with AI.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.480913925749753e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Divij is always busy, Motwani said, \\\"It does not feel stressful because he's doing it in a very fun way.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Itishis fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Inevitably, a busy kid might decide to drop some of these activities.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's OK.  Alexa Groff was a little \\\"bummed\\\" when her daughter, Taylor, wanted to quit volleyball to prioritize other extracurriculars.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Alexa\", \"score\": 0.9999999956544343, \"rank\": 3.4699985565022767e-09, \"text\": \"Alexa\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Alexa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Alexa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Groff supported her decision.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want her to figure things out on her own, but know that I am there for whatever she needs me for,\\\" Groff, a state science fair director in Iowa, told BI.\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2704, \"end\": 2708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.990960790568975, \"rank\": 0.009121659607074482, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3592646868491829e-11, \"text\": \"BI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many students at ISEF pursued solutions to problems in their community.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISEF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Science_and_Engineering_Fair\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, Oahu resident Maddux Alexander Springer, one of the top winners,investigated tumors that were killing sea turtleson his shores.\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2806, \"end\": 2810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oahu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oahu\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oahu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oahu\"}, {\"begin\": 2820, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Maddux\", \"score\": 0.9999999912993189, \"rank\": 8.700704486364574e-09, \"text\": \"Maddux\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Maddux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Maddux\"}, {\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\", \"score\": 0.9999851694132467, \"rank\": 1.3748907788706623e-05, \"text\": \"Alexander\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_the_Great\"}, {\"begin\": 2837, \"end\": 2845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Springer\", \"score\": 0.9978469514661144, \"rank\": 0.00207967286627788, \"text\": \"Springer\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Springer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Springer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AndEstrada's daughter, Pauline, studied the herbicide-resistant weeds plaguing the farms surrounding her Fresno home.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Fowler\", \"score\": 0.9995689136930781, \"rank\": 0.0004311084785331499, \"text\": \"Pauline\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Fowler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Fowler\"}, {\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fresno_River\", \"score\": 0.5288866902846875, \"rank\": 0.70176884574848, \"text\": \"Fresno\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fresno_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fresno_River\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Estrada partially attributes her kids' communityengagement to theirpublic school, where they grew up with people from different backgrounds.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"score\": 0.7953820283154115, \"rank\": 0.17127396054660346, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You will learn a lot from being there,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They really know how to deal with different types of people, different ethnicities, different cultures.\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I always tell them, you just be respectful of everybody.\\\"\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Travel can help foster compassion and curiosity too, Motwani said.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The more exposure I give them, the more curious they are, the more they learn, the more they question.\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's nothing to do with science,\\\" Motwani said.\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you look at a lot of his projects, the heart of it is: How do I help?\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How do I make a difference in people's lives?\\\"\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, kids also need to learn resilience.\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Groff said that being a single mom, she led by example for her daughter.\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her seeing failure and the resilience of not quitting - I think that's something really important,\\\" Groff said.\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's taught her you might get sick of it and you might hate it.\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 4050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pause and come back.\", \"from\": 4051, \"to\": 4071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like a brand new day.\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have a crappy day, go to bed, you wake up fresh.\\\"\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The moms said their children were motivated to muscle through when their science fair projects got tough, simply because they liked doing it.\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than pushing their kids to win or get the best GPA, the parents said they tried to foster that intrinsic motivation.\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4351, \"end\": 4354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\", \"score\": 0.9999999999768079, \"rank\": 2.326813282688268e-11, \"text\": \"GPA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our lives actually revolve around science fair because this is something that my kids enjoy doing,\\\" Estrada said.\", \"from\": 4422, \"to\": 4536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4523, \"end\": 4530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"score\": 0.7953820283154115, \"rank\": 0.17127396054660346, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eating healthy, exercising, and getting enough sleep are crucial for anyone.\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All three habits can improve longevity, reduce the risk of myriad diseases, and even give you an edge in cognitive functioning.\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He knows how important it is for us to get a proper night's sleep,\\\" Motwani said of her son.\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just to make sure he does, though, she's asked him to leave his phone and laptop with her around midnight during his high school years.\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Otherwise, he would work on science fair projects until 2 a.m., she said.\", \"from\": 4975, \"to\": 5048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Estrada's husband Dexter took a different approach, she said, and simply cut the kids' internet access at midnight using Google's Family Link app.\", \"from\": 5050, \"to\": 5196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5050, \"end\": 5057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"score\": 0.7953820283154115, \"rank\": 0.17127396054660346, \"text\": \"Estrada\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinoy_Big_Brother:_Kumunity_Season_10\"}, {\"begin\": 5068, \"end\": 5074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dexter_Morgan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.0987200074962425e-11, \"text\": \"Dexter\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dexter_Morgan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dexter_Morgan\"}, {\"begin\": 5171, \"end\": 5177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9999784901868773, \"rank\": 2.151026799246435e-05, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Motwani says she also has to keep an eye on her son's nutrition, reminding him to eat a fruit and a vegetable each day.\", \"from\": 5198, \"to\": 5317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is an exciting time.\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like he wants to conquer the world, which is awesome,\\\" Motwani said.\", \"from\": 5346, \"to\": 5421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But making sure he stays healthy - that's good.\\\"\", \"from\": 5422, \"to\": 5471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jump to\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5480, \"entities\": []}]}"